# Title: imperative mood, ≤72 chars, no period
# Example: Add gameplay validator for mystery solvability checks
#
# Body (optional): explain WHAT and WHY, not HOW. Wrap at 72 chars.
# Leave a blank line between title and body.
#
# ─── Good title examples ────────────────────────────────────────────
#   Add mystery generator with RAG pipeline
#   Fix missing API key startup error
#   Remove duplicate data model definitions
#   Update requirements to mark optional dependencies
#   Rename demo output directory to match production path
#
# ─── Rules ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
#   • Start with a capital verb: Add, Fix, Remove, Update, Rename,
#     Refactor, Extract, Move, Document, Test, Wire, Validate
#   • No "Add files via upload" — describe what the files do
#   • Body answers: why this change? what problem does it solve?
#   • Reference issues/PRs at the bottom: Closes #12, See #34
#
